        "product_description": {
            "value": [
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "Get your child into the holiday spirit with the Blue's Clues Kids Christmas Stocking. <br/><br/>This cute felt stocking is embossed with a seasonal snowflake print and features Blue from the hit children's show. It's constructed of soft but durable felt that will last for years to come and comes with a hang loop that can easily be attached to any mantle.<br/><br/>The stocking itself is very lightweight and measures 15.5\" in length, so you can stuff it to the brim with toys, games, and accessories before Santa arrives and it will hang safely overnight. It has a seasonal embossed snowflake pattern that will brighten up any living room or den. If your child is a Blue's Clues fanatic, then this Christmas stocking is the perfect home decor accessory this holiday season.",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                }
            ],
